<font color="#FF0000">WHERE'S THE ENEMY????</font><br>
<tt>Sun Aug 10 14:15:15 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Okay Spatz, crawl yourself out from under that leaky Chevy (should have bought a Ford)!  That is providing that you are not too fat to get under a Chevy... or to old and decrepit to crawl out from under one.<br>
There are legions of veterans out here who want to kick your butt or pick your brain (the first option is probably most preferable if you are the type who prefers quantity or large targets!)<br>
I am interested in where, how and when you decided not to march off to war.  Was it a tough decision or an easy one?  Did you ever doubt yourself?<br>
War protesters have forced me to push all my stuff up on the firing line on the opposing hill, with some kind of self defense objective in mind.  Being in the attack mode keeps me away from the center of the continuum.  Are you guilty of that?<br>
I hate killing people, everyday!<br>
I hate Losing friends, everyday!<br>
I hate being a sucker, everyday!<br>
I hate being rejected, everyday!<br>
I am angered by the realization that I would go again if called.<br><br>
See you in the valley, Sleepy Head!<br><br>
Mustang Two Four<br><br>
P.S.  Shine your sandals, brasso your Peace symbol and trim your split ends (there may be an inspection in ranks.)<br>
Also, try and show some respect for your elders... I am three years and two days older than you... Junior!<br>
Ed
